Elsevier Freedom versus Elsevier Subscribed

Elsevier broken down by Freedom collection and Subscribed collection. The Freedom Collection is a list of ~1850 active titles (2350 titles in all, including renamed, transferred, discontinued and forthcoming titles) that any institution subscribing to Science Direct Complete gets access to.
